00:43:13.820 --> 00:43:17.240 position:56%
And it stops all of those particles.

00:43:17.240 --> 00:43:20.490
Unless you're on top of a mountain,
or traveling in an airplane,

00:43:20.490 --> 00:43:23.270
you can't really measure much
of these types of particles.

00:43:23.270 --> 00:43:25.220
They don't make it to the ground.

00:43:25.220 --> 00:43:30.060
But if you're an astronaut
and if you're out in the ISS

00:43:30.060 --> 00:43:35.180
or even traveling to the moon,
