00:44:33.560 --> 00:44:36.190 position:56%
So, that's a really critical aspect.

00:44:36.190 --> 00:44:39.450
And that is one of the biggest
challenges of traveling to,

00:44:39.450 --> 00:44:41.520
especially to some place like Mars.

00:44:41.520 --> 00:44:45.860
Now, when you go to Mars, Mars
doesn't have the magnetic field,

00:44:45.860 --> 00:44:49.500
but it also has an
extremely thin atmosphere.

00:44:49.500 --> 00:44:54.210 position:56%
To put that in perspective, the
atmosphere of Mars is about as thick

00:44:54.210 --> 00:44:57.600
as our atmosphere at 100,000 feet.

00:44:57.600 --> 00:45:02.650
Higher than any of the
commercial airplanes flying.

00:45:02.650 --> 00:45:05.110
You know you've see
the movie "The Martian"

