in particular how it
impacts our technology.

00:46:01.230 --> 00:46:05.770
But in terms of flying
through the solar system,

00:46:05.770 --> 00:46:09.600 position:56%
these particle events are really the
most critical part of space weather

00:46:09.600 --> 00:46:11.260
that we have to pay attention to.

00:46:11.260 --> 00:46:12.720
And this is the biggest challenge

00:46:12.720 --> 00:46:17.890
that we have going
to a place like Mars.

00:46:17.890 --> 00:46:22.660
And for the moon also, it's
still a huge challenge.

00:46:22.660 --> 00:46:24.200
But especially Mars.

00:46:24.200 --> 00:46:26.700
Because really it's
